categories: Category:Starships of the resurgent Sith Empire

nodes.text: A warship of the Sith Empire participated in the Battle of Corellia in 3640 BBY, during the Galactic War with the Galactic Republic, and was heavily damaged during the battle. It clipped a high-rise tower in Corellia's capital of Coronet City, collapsing several floors and nearly toppling the entire tower.
The Imperial warship was first mentioned in the Codex entry for the Beharen Droid Factory in Star Wars: The Old Republic, a video game released by BioWare in 2011.
